title: Emily Ratajkowski Strips Down to Her Underwear to Tease a 'Secret Project'
text:
Emily Ratajkowski Strips Down to Her Underwear to Tease a 'Secret Project' by Latifah Muhammad 2:42 PM   Emily Ratajkowski Strips Down to Her Underwear to Tease a 'Secret Project' Emily Ratajkowski showed off her toned body in a racy new pic while teasing a "secret project." On Thursday, the 25-year-old model-actress took to Instagram with an animated snapshot of herself lying down in a white bra and panties, captioned, "Secret project in NYC today coming to you March 2017." A video posted by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Jan 19, 2017 at 1:16pm PST While she didn't provide any more details on the project, Ratajkowski was spotted modeling in her underwear on the streets of New York City on Friday. Photo: Getty Images MORE: Emily Ratajkowski Posts Another Entirely Nude Photo on Instagram Ratajkowski, who is best known for appearing in the music videos for Robin Thicke’s "Blurred Lines" and Maroon 5's "Love Somebody," certainly isn’t shy about showing off her figure on social media, but she’s not all about revealing shots. The London-born beauty also shared pics from her Vogue Spain photo shoot with her 10.7 million Instagram followers. A photo posted by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Jan 18, 2017 at 3:27am PST A photo posted by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Jan 18, 2017 at 10:34am PST A photo posted by Emily Ratajkowski (@emrata) on Jan 18, 2017 at 1:18pm PST WATCH: Emily Ratajkowski Dances to Salt-N-Pepa in the Sexiest Monokini of All Time for 'Love' Magazine 
Ratajkowski is so comfortable in her skin, she even handles wardrobe malfunctions like a pro. Despite revealing more than she intended while on the red carpet at InStyle's 18th Annual Post-Golden Globes Party earlier this month, Ratajkowski didn't stop smiling and posing for photos.
